<figureCitation id="131C0C90FFB2FFE5FF0AFEC7067AFEC0" box="[151,279,330,355]" captionStart="FIGURES 27–40" captionStartId="21.[151,264,1866,1889]" captionTargetBox="[175,1408,209,1827]" captionTargetId="figure@21.[151,1436,193,1845]" captionTargetPageId="21" captionText="FIGURES 27–40. Habitus of species of Penthimia. 27–28. Holotype male P. neoattenuata sp. nov., dorsal and lateral view. 29–30. P.quadrinotata Distant topotypes, color variation; 31–32. Holotype male P.ribhoi sp. nov., dorsal and lateral view.33– 34. Holotype male P.shyadrica sp. nov., dorsal and lateral view.35–36.Holotype male P.spiculata sp. nov., dorsal and lateral view.37–40. P.tumida sp. nov. 37–38. Holotype male, dorsal and lateral view; 39–40. Paratypefemale dorsal and lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1135484/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Figs 35–36</figureCitation>
